@startuml
title System Context
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "User" as User
node "Browser" as Browser
component "React Frontend" as Frontend
component "NestJS API" as Backend

database "Fuseki (SPARQL RDF store)" as Fuseki
cloud "LLM Provider (OpenAI or Ollama)" as LLM
folder "Uploads (PDF files)" as Uploads

User --> Browser : interact
Browser --> Frontend : UI
Frontend --> Backend : REST + SSE (JWT)
Backend --> Fuseki : SPARQL query/update
Backend --> Uploads : store/read PDFs
Backend --> LLM : chat + summaries
@enduml
